&lt;P class=MsoNormal 0pt? 0in **Zowie**?MARGIN:&gt;&lt;SPAN Gothic?? ?Century FONT-FAMILY: **Zowie**?FONT-SIZE: 10pt;&gt;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;SPAN Gothic?? ?Century FONT-FAMILY: **Zowie**?FONT-SIZE: 10pt;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;SPAN Gothic?? ?Century FONT-FAMILY: **Zowie**?FONT-SIZE: 10pt;&gt;You as a class will have the option to replace items that are marked as “no changes planned at this time” with new items or leave them on the list.&amp;nbsp; Please understand that leaving them on the list does not mean that they will eventually be implemented however it does mean that the class as a whole still feels that these are valid issues and would like implementation eventually.&amp;nbsp; One thing to note, we will not be responding to requests as to why something is classified the way it is.&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&#xD;
