&lt;P class=MsoNormal 0in mso-layout-grid-align: l0 mso-list: tab-stops: list -0.25in; TEXT-INDENT: 0pt **SMURF**?MARGIN: level2 lfo3; none; 57.0pt? 57pt;&gt;&lt;SPAN mso-bidi-font-family: mso-fareast-font-family: Symbol? Symbol; **SMURF**?FONT-FAMILY:&gt;&lt;SPAN Ignore? **SMURF**?mso-list:&gt;·&lt;SPAN Roman?? New ?Times 7pt **SMURF**?FONT:&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; &lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;SPAN ?Century Gothic?? **SMURF**?mso-bidi-font-family:&gt;Make it easier for players to properly /tar the Beastlord or their warder&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&#xD;
&lt;P class=MsoNormal 0in mso-layout-grid-align: l0 mso-list: tab-stops: list -0.25in; TEXT-INDENT: 0pt **SMURF**?MARGIN: level2 lfo3; none; 57.0pt? 57pt;&gt;&lt;SPAN mso-bidi-font-family: mso-fareast-font-family: Symbol? Symbol; **SMURF**?FONT-FAMILY:&gt;&lt;SPAN Ignore? **SMURF**?mso-list:&gt;·&lt;SPAN Roman?? New ?Times 7pt **SMURF**?FONT:&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; &lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;SPAN ?Century Gothic?? **SMURF**?mso-bidi-font-family:&gt;Add an exclamation point or something to the front of beastlord warder names so that by typing /target tast" the person will target Tastian, but by typing say "/target !tast" the player would then target Tastian`s warder instead.&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&#xD;
